mode-custom-css:
.rbox-t2v .syndicatedItem .branding {color:#555;} .rbox-t2v .syndicatedItem .thumbnail-emblem {display:none;} .rbox-t2v .trc_sponsored_overlay {display:none}
.rbox-t2v {margin-bottom: 10px;}

.autosized-generated-2r .trc_rbox_header {	height: auto;	background-repeat: no-repeat;}.autosized-generated-2r .logoDiv a {	vertical-align: baseline;}.autosized-generated-2r > .logoDiv {	margin-top: -10px;}.autosized-generated-2r .logoDiv a span {	display: inline;	color: #000000;	font-weight: normal;	font-size: 11px;}.autosized-generated-2r .video-label-box {	min-height: 48.0px;}.autosized-generated-2r .videoCube .video-label-box .video-title {	text-decoration: none;}.autosized-generated-2r .videoCube.thumbnail_under .label-box-overlay {	display: inline;	background-color: #6b6b6b;	opacity: 0.75;	filter: alpha(opacity=75.0);}.autosized-generated-2r .video-label-box .branding {	display: block;}.autosized-generated-2r .syndicatedItem .branding {	line-height: 16.0px;}

.grid-4x2 .trc_rbox_header {	height: auto;	background-repeat: no-repeat;}.grid-4x2 .logoDiv a {	vertical-align: baseline;}.grid-4x2 > .logoDiv {	margin-top: -10px;}.grid-4x2 .logoDiv a span {	color: #999;	font-weight: normal;	font-size: 10px;}.grid-4x2 .video-label-box {	min-height: 48.0px;}.grid-4x2 .videoCube .video-label-box .video-title {	text-decoration: none;}.grid-4x2 .videoCube.thumbnail_under .label-box-overlay {	background-color: #ffffff;	opacity: 0.8;	filter: alpha(opacity=80.0);}.grid-4x2 .video-label-box .branding {	display: block;}.grid-4x2 .syndicatedItem .branding {	line-height: 16.0px;}
